ership programs were still intact. He remembered how roughly he was treated=
 and how he was slammed into the CR chamber. To top it off he was always cr=
anky when he woke up. "What is the meaning of this travesty?" he yelled. He=
 saw Predacon emblem on Attilla so he knew thought he wasn't a POW. "Is thi=
s any way to treat one of the Predacons best training units?" his record of=
 service would have spoke for itself if he hadn't erased it when he left th=
e Predacons to start his own unit.
